## Project Structure

```
cmd/app/               # binary entrypoint
internal/
  app/                 # dependency wiring and server startup
  entity/              # domain structs
  usecase/             # business logic
  controller/http/     # HTTP handlers, router, middleware
  repo/
    persistent/        # DB layer
    webapi/            # external HTTP calls
pkg/
  logger/              # Logger interface + implementation
  client/              # shared HTTP client
  constants/           # application-wide constants
  utils/               # shared utilities
config/                # config loader (Viper + godotenv)
```

