## Environment Variables

Copy `.env.example` to `.env` and fill in the values.

| Variable | Description | Default |
|----------|-------------|---------|
| `SERVER_PORT` | HTTP server port | `8080` |
| `VERSION` | Application version | `v0.1.0` |
| `LOG_LEVEL` | Log level (`debug`, `info`, `warn`, `error`) | `info` |
{{- if or (eq .DB "postgres-gorm") (eq .DB "postgres-sqlc") (eq .DB "postgres-raw")}}
| `DB_HOST` | PostgreSQL host | `localhost` |
| `DB_PORT` | PostgreSQL port | `5432` |
| `DB_USER` | PostgreSQL user | `postgres` |
| `DB_PASSWORD` | PostgreSQL password | â€” |
| `DB_NAME` | Database name | `{{.Name}}` |
| `DB_SSL_MODE` | SSL mode (`disable`, `require`) | `disable` |
{{- end}}
{{- if or (eq .DB "sqlite-gorm") (eq .DB "sqlite-raw")}}
| `DB_PATH` | SQLite file path | `./data.db` |
{{- end}}
{{- if or (eq .DB "mysql-gorm") (eq .DB "mysql-raw") (eq .DB "mysql-sqlc")}}
| `DB_HOST` | MySQL host | `localhost` |
